{"tid":1779972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會計界巴打好波，民主派大勝。","createTime":"2019-12-12T04:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T06:52:41.000Z","uid":171506,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf38e0f69e97cad2222908055cecf128bf76ed88","tid":1779972,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%81%B8-7-%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%9D%E5%8F%96-6-%E5%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2581%25B8-7-%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%258F%2596-6-%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=9a9ea7cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2581%25B8-7-%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%258F%2596-6-%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&h=4c9ef9eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%81%B8-7-%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%9D%E5%8F%96-6-%E5%B8%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"cd7247ccad844a0b404489c6e81d715900b045fe","tid":1779972,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"香港會計師公會理事選舉，日前公布選舉結果，6 名民主派候人全數當選，於一共 7 席的理事席位中，壓倒性地取得 6 席，保守派只險守住 1 席。成功當選理事的民主派候選人李淑儀表示，選舉結果表明了會計師行業於區議會選舉之後的態度。由於今年投票人數為歷年之最，且首次突破一萬人，有意見認為高投票率對民主派有利。<br />\n<br />\n今年 11 月 24 日區議會選舉民主派取得壓到性勝利，熱烈選舉氣氛亦蔓延至會計師公會理事選舉。該會擁有逾 4 萬名會員，屬本港人數最多的專業團體之一，而公會理事會的 21 個席位中，有 14 席由會員一人一選出，由於當中 7 席的任期明年才完結，故今屆只選出其餘 7 席。今屆共有 15 人參選，包括「民主進步會計師」派出的６人名單：李淑儀、李健恆、馮領業、梁文俊、蔡啟昇、張煒麟，６人悉數當選，他們的參選政綱包括一人一票選會長及副會長，推動公會根據財務狀況考慮寬免會費，及建議政府就修訂《逃犯條例》爭議作出檢討，成立獨立調查委員會等。<br />\n<br />\n保守派 7 名參選人分別為賴耘峯、梁思傑、吳錦華、湯志超、謝海發、黃劍文及阮肇斌，只得梁思傑當選。另外並無明確取向的張文祺與潘文思怡亦告落選，後者為電視動畫廣告為人熟悉的「會計妹」。7 名當選人將於明年 1 月 1 日履新，任期兩年。"},{"pid":"a6881009c1571d74f28167524b3a6e60e6682557","tid":1779972,"uid":294221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27Y0Qxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27Y0Qxo.jpg&h=f8d2ca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人嘅最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n專攻BNO平權<br />\n幫手解答BNO問題<br />\n<br />\n#MagnitskyAct #BNOisBritish #WeAreBritish #RightTheWrong #SaveBritish #SOSHK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJoin us: <a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=975178b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"},{"pid":"602b5cc8ddb31241222d549914205b98fe37bb5b","tid":1779972,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以光復埋保險界"},{"pid":"247b05b338971a0987b3ab800e2bed206a173f92","tid":1779972,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"602b5cc8ddb31241222d549914205b98fe37bb5b","tid":1779972,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以光復埋保險界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"希望光復多幾界"},{"pid":"e4e79bc0a9c99d3234bd4da2c4c6c9f7e75af89e","tid":1779972,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54f4be7e33c0ed1724e6caf23326349b1956f3aa","tid":1779972,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s